OUTPUT WATERMARKING

All outputs generated by the VetIOS inference and intelligence systems
are watermarked with cryptographic fingerprints identifying the
originating tenant, session, and platform version. Removal or
circumvention of these fingerprints is a violation of this Licence
and applicable law.

